  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will compare the efficacy and safety of a single dose of a lidocaine 8 mg +
      cetylpyridimium chloride (CPC) 2 mg lozenge with a single dose of a lidocaine 1 mg + CPC 2 mg
      lozenge in the treatment of sore throat due to a common cold.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
