  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with sore throat due to an upper respiratory tract infection, with recent
             onset (within 48 hours)

          -  Sore throat of at least moderate pain intensity

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  - History of hypersensitivity to any of the study drugs and listed excipients or to
             drugs of similar chemical classes

          -  Evidence of mouth breathing or severe coughing

          -  Evidence of overt oropharyngeal bacterial or fungal infection or evidence of lower
             respirator tract infection

          -  Severe renal, liver or cardiac impairment

          -  Severe lung disease
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
    <gender>All</gender>
